Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down a difficult road\Nfilled with endless struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you are going\Nfollowing someone else's map?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An insightful crow comes along\Nto tear up the map
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now open your eyes and\Ntake a look at the truth (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to lose,\Nso let's GO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh!\NJust go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go with Fukusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go after Idate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:01:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Right! 					– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Idate!\NThe ocean is that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going!\NCome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! There’s no way\NI’m going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that kid think\Nhe’s doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he’s run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate’s been like that\Nfrom long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, kind of…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Race is On!\NTrouble on the High Seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he’d run away,\Nthat bastard Idate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing him this long,\Nyou must’ve figured this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to let him run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!\Nldate isn’t that kind of kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Boss! 					– Boss…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in Idate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Retainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think\Nyou’re going to settle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've turned this grand traditional\Nfestival into a mere farce…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And worse,\Nin the presence of the lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, the race has just begun.\NPlease watch it until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you insist that much,\Nyou had better win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll ask for the dissolution\Nof your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed! I’m a man of my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Idate loses,\Nyou may do anything you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How like Wasabi’s Jirocho.\NSuch confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on you, Idate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A starving thief, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid trying to act tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that little thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can’t even peel an apple,\Ncan you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edged tools aren’t\Nfor hurting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have anywhere to go,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Jirocho of Wasabi\Nof Degarashi Port.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasabi…Jirocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?\NWhy don’t you come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just tried to…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone on the verge of starvation\Nwill make such mistakes…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t hold it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah…this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it to you. 					Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever do stupid things\Nlike stealing…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!\NMake me your henchman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean…\Ncould you please, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate…\NMy name is Idate Morino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go then, Idate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, just trust in me!\NI will win, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can catch up\Nto him in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s too late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can’t win if\Nhe’s this far from the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he may've planned to come\Nthis way from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we can stop them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would’ve thought\Nthey’d be escorting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Lucky!\NNow I can pay them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what they did to us\Nduring the Chunin Exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two go ahead.\NI’ll keep them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we’ve caught up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Why on earth\Ndid you come this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\Nlt’s none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda attitude is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren’t aware of it, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of Genjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve already been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Looks like\NI’ve been tricked by Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don’t go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be still!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll get pulled up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A double Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty elaborate trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! It’s your fault that\Nwe’re going through all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop! Stop, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Ninja tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an unnecessary help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say unnecessary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey bastard, can’t you even\Nthank us for saving you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me\Nbecause it’s your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Naruto. He’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don’t want to die,\Nyou should stay close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you going back\Nto Port Degarashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, I’m heading north from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,North? Is it faster that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…\NI really don’t trust this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why Ninja are no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a strong seasonal wind blows\Nacross this ocean…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the starting point, I watched the clouds\Nand realized it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the wind was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,\Nat the port to the north,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s an ocean current\Nthat flows straight to Nagi Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This part is different from you guys.\NRight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it’s getting a bit rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don’t push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head more towards the south!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that’ll take up quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get on the land,\Nno one can run faster than I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My victory is already set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I taste salt in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that far out on the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the halfway point --\NNagi Island where Modoroki shrine is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get there within an hour.\NWait for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man, I’m here!\Nlt's Idate from the Wasabi Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I’ve been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll need you to lend me a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I have it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the fastest boat around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Boss Jirocho has done\Nso much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, don’t lose to Wagarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fed up with how\Nthey handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be down on my luck now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm Idate, the number one\Nhenchman of the Wasabi Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest easy and leave it all to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should start seeing\NNagi Island’s port soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can get there\Nbefore Fukusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naruto…\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Idate…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s definitely not\Nan ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can run extraordinarily fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could have received\Nspecial training…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of training?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, maybe he’d been\Nin a hidden village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy that stupid can’t be a Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s talking here?!\NYou're as stupid as he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it to the final round\Nof the Chunin Exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the final round\Nof the Chunin Exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that’ s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren’t interrupted\Nin the middle of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have won the tournament\Nand become a Chunin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must have had\Na darn easy proctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, the level of\Nthe Chunin Exam has dropped…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate, so you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate Morino.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morino… That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t the proctor\Nof the first test….?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, you rotten runts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the proctor for\Nthe first test of the Chunin Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Morino Ibiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morino… Ibiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother I-Ibiki is alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, he’s alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me a weird problem\Non the 10th question…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?\NHe really is alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What’s this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\Nit’s right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let’s get started\Non our plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto and I will chase them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, take care of Idate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it better to run…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll cover you. Remove the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I have to cut these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I lost them all that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lend me that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hand it to me, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, this is more important\Nthan my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way\NI’ll let you use it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be saying\Nstuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura! They are just clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the real one can attack you,\Nso don’t worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real ones are hiding among\Nthe clones! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke! Guide us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate, stay close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! I don’t want a Ninja’s help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still saying that\Nin this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A clone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Clone for clone!\N– Clone for clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, they got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work! Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shadow Clone kid\Nis troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next plan, Kagari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Style!\NBlack Rain Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke! They’ve changed\Ninto Water Clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!\NI’ll get rid of them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Tiger Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlucky…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Having you stay will be\Na burden to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke, what can we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the fire is this strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll have to dive in\Nto the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, we can swim\Nto the port of Nagi Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! There’s no other option left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate, can you swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! I’ll cover you, so go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This smoke should help you\Nescape unnoticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are tricking me into\Nbecoming a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re trying to get\Nthe enemy’s attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don’t trust Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having you stay will be\Na burden to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Having you stay\Nis a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way we will\Nuse you as a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idate! Duck down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me Idate!\NI promise I’ll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakura…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll follow you right after!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we withdraw now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most enjoyable part\Nis still left undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, they are\Nunexpectedly tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But we won’t\Nlet them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I should be okay here…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Idate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taught you so many times\Nnot to trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool, you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your promise,\Nits a true heart give me courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always I feel it\Nthe precious time with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your still shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the wind that blows\Ntowards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city lights are like pieces of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hold us together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Each one of us glows differently,”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you say laughingly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you look most dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a comet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the rainbow after the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bring light into my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being lost can be the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s promise we won’t cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... like a shooting star,\Nwe do go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool or whatever…\Nlt doesn't matter now how you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This race is not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never know unless\Nyou try 'til the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jirocho believes in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to stall and act cool,\Nwhy don't you show some guts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Run Idate Run!\NNagi Island Awaits!
